description: Holiday Isle's frozen Florida Keys legend — banana, blackberry, and rum over crushed ice.
author: John "Tiki John" Ebert (1972, Holiday Isle Tiki Bar, Islamorada, Florida Keys)
year: 1972
venue: Holiday Isle Tiki Bar, Islamorada, Florida Keys
